title: Daily Green
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Uses primarily local and organic, including all greens, tempeh and bread. Some menu items are waffles, waffle cones, salads, and sandwiches, of which some are vegan such as tempeh sandwiches, seitan, a walnut lentil burger, and vegetable sandwiches like a dried green tomato sandwich. Uses separate cookware. Confirmed open Oct 2015.
